narratives.question_text: What knowledge, skills, and insights did you develop by taking this course?
comments: I developed speaking, listening, and writing skills in the Indonesian language. I also fathered my vocabulary and learned how to speak in the past tense in Indonesian.
I learned how to learn a language better and advanced my Indonesian speaking and writing skills.
i learned about indonesian culture and gained a better understanding of the culture.
Furthered and expanded my education in the Indonesian language.

It is very engaging and Bu Dinny does a great job getting everyone involved. 

Maybe more worksheets to practice writing.

narratives.question_text: Would you recommend this course to another student? Please explain.
comments: Yes I would. If you're looking to learn a language you normally wouldn't have the opportunity to elsewhere this is a fun language to learn.
Yes, I really enjoyed this course, learning Indonesian, the small group class, and the professor.
Yes absolutely. Both the Indonesian Prefessors are great and the course is very enjoyable.
Yes definitely. Indonesian is such an enjoyable language and class. The culture is so interesting to learn about.
